properties.SQL:
SELECT original.*, enrichment.* 
FROM original 
LEFT OUTER JOIN enrichment 
ON original.id = enrichment.id

SELECT original.*, enrichment.* 
FROM original 
FULL JOIN enrichment
ON original.date = enrichment.date
WHERE original.date = enrichment.date

    temp VARCHAR(50));
